    <item>
      <title>墨西哥领跑者预计 Pemex 将于 2025 年进行债务再融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/mexico-s-frontrunner-sees-pemex-refinancing-debt-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥主要总统候选人克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆 (Claudia Sheinbaum) 表示，她预计全球负债最重的石油生产商墨西哥国家石油公司 (Petroleo Mexicanos) 将在 2025 年债券到期之前对其债券进行再融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/mexico-s-frontrunner-sees-pemex-refinancing-debt-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 00:07:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普封口费陪审团现已定于周一在纽约进行开庭辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/trump-hush-money-jury-now-set-for-opening-arguments-in-ny-monday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的首次刑事审判的陪审团选拔工作于周五完成，为周一纽约一桩指控这位前总统在 2016 年大选前伪造商业记录以隐瞒性丑闻的案件的开庭辩论奠定了基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/trump-hush-money-jury-now-set-for-opening-arguments-in-ny-monday</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 22:55:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗与以色列的一周袭击标志着中东“游戏规则改变者”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/week-of-iran-israel-strikes-marks-a-mideast-game-changer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗和以色列之间长达数十年的影子战争中最激烈的一周之一周五以轻松结束，此前德黑兰宣布击败了以色列无人机对其领土的小规模袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/week-of-iran-israel-strikes-marks-a-mideast-game-changer</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 22:24:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>涡轮机如何制动纽约海上风电项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/ny-offshore-wind-projects-stall-over-lack-of-turbine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚刚起步的美国海上风电产业周五再次遭受打击——但由于一个新的原因：没有所需的涡轮机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/ny-offshore-wind-projects-stall-over-lack-of-turbine</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 22:22:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索尼收购派拉蒙的交易将受到更多监管审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/sony-deal-for-paramount-would-draw-added-regulatory-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿分析师称，收购派拉蒙全球公司（其中包括日本索尼集团公司）的交易预计将受到审查外国买家媒体购买的美国监管机构的审查，以及竞争监管机构的审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/sony-deal-for-paramount-would-draw-added-regulatory-scrutiny</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 22:04:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾希望美国和日本接管中国关注的铁路协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/philippines-wants-us-japan-to-take-over-rail-deal-eyed-by-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名负责菲律宾货运铁路项目的官员表示，菲律宾货运铁路项目可能会在美国和日本的支持下建设，马尼拉在放弃与中国的融资谈判后正在寻求替代融资协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/philippines-wants-us-japan-to-take-over-rail-deal-eyed-by-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
